delayed mixing of FG and SG binaries\nfor the differences between the kinematics of the two populations are\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2018 05:47:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
