ity-based estimators is discussed, demonstrating the advantages of\ndetermining the centrality with energy deposited near beam rapidity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2018 10:18:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2019 15:08:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-17"}
