st in material properties as well as the\nphase boundary toughness on the outcome of this competition. In the case of\ncrack nucleation, the crack length shows an equally strong dependency on these\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2018 15:07:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
