conds when 10 clients arrive each minute\n(Client/minute), the average time delay is 140 milliseconds when the video\nlengths are 30, 60 and 90. Meanwhile, the failure probability for obtaining the\nfirst segment of the video remains zero when the number of arrived requests is\nset to 2, 4, 6, 8 and 10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2018 21:30:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-21"}
